description:
The Revolution is the second studio album from Christian rock band Inhabited.
It was released on July 12, 2005 on Fervent Records. Four songs were released as radio singles: &quot;Open My Eyes&quot;, &quot;One More Night&quot;, &quot;Revolution&quot; and &quot;Rescue Me&quot;, which charted in the top 10 on Christian rock radio and top 20 on Christian music charts.

Track listing:

   1. &quot;Open My Eyes&quot;
   2. &quot;Rescue Me&quot;
   3. &quot;Everybody Listen&quot;
   4. &quot;One More Night&quot;
   5. &quot;I Run to You&quot;
   6. &quot;You Are My Peace&quot;
   7. &quot;Save My Life&quot;
   8. &quot;Angel (Where Are You)&quot;
   9. &quot;If We Could Love&quot;
  10. &quot;Memories&quot;
  11. &quot;Revolution&quot;


